author: rhuijben
msg: Instead of calculating and verifying the pristine copy of a file before
updating it, calculate and verify the used text base (base/revert/copied)
stream while applying the delta using the new stream checksum api.
This avoids reading the pristine version of a file twice.
(handler_baton): Add 3 variables for calculating the checksum.
(window_handler): When finished ok or with an error verify the checksum.
(apply_textdelta): Stop verifying if the checksum in the entries file is
correct. Instead compare the value with the expected value and setup a
checksum stream to validate while applying the text delta.
